    {
      "inventory_id": "Boots1",
      "additional_text": "Runeforged Quickslip Shoes\n1. +77 to [Evasion] Rating\n2. +22 to maximum [EnergyShield|Energy Shield]\n3. 99% increased [Evasion] and [EnergyShield|Energy Shield]\n4. +45% to [Resistances|Lightning Resistance]\n5. Gain [Deflect|Deflection Rating] equal to 22% of [Evasion|Evasion Rating]\n6. 5% increased Movement Speed\n7. 8% increased Movement Speed while Sprinting\n8. [ShamanOnlyMods|Bonded]: 50% increased [StunRecovery|Stun Recovery]\n9. [ShamanOnlyMods|Bonded]: 10% increased [CooldownRecovery|Cooldown Recovery Rate]",
      "level_interval": [
        75,
        100
      ],
      "slot_x": 0,
      "slot_y": 0
    },
    {
      "inventory_id": "Gloves1",
      "additional_text": "Runeforged Vaal Wraps\n1. Adds 23 to 37 [Cold] damage to [Attack|Attacks]\n2. 39% increased [Projectile] Speed\n3. 39% increased [Projectile] Damage\n4. [Gain] 1% of Damage as [Gain|Extra] Damage of a random [ElementalDamage|Element] per\n[Rune] Socketed in [Equipped] Items\n5. Can roll Marksman modifiers\n6. [ShamanOnlyMods|Bonded]: 20% increased [ElementalDamage|Elemental Damage]\n7. [ShamanOnlyMods|Bonded]: 20% increased [Projectile] Damage",
      "level_interval": [
        75,
