      "additional_text": "Warmonger Bow\n1. 252% increased [Physical] Damage\n2. +194 to [Accuracy|Accuracy] Rating\n3. +25% to [CriticalDamageBonus|Critical Damage Bonus]\n4. +4 to Level of all [Projectile] Skills\n5. +198% [SurpassChance|Surpassing] chance to fire an additional Arrow\n6. +1 Suffix Modifier allowed\n7. Bow [Attack|Attacks] fire an additional Arrow\n8. [Gain] 5% of Damage as Extra Damage of all [ElementalDamage|Elements]\n9. [ShamanOnlyMods|Bonded]: 20% increased [Projectile] Speed\n10. [ShamanOnlyMods|Bonded]: 8% chance to gain an additional random [Charges|Charge] when you gain a Charge",
